53:52.521 --> 53:57.930
And what it is, it's my comments and the original papers.

53:58.050 --> 53:59.392
It's no real book.

54:02.237 --> 54:02.537
Excellent.

54:02.558 --> 54:05.082
And you were going to get me a copy of an essay, I think.

54:05.102 --> 54:05.783
Yes, I will.

54:06.364 --> 54:11.492
